<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 09:09:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>受制裁的油轮Liteyny Prospect停靠在中国以卸载俄罗斯石油</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/sanctioned-tanker-liteyny-prospect-docks-china-offload-russian-oil-2024-03-07/</link><description>据两位知情人士透露，受到制裁的俄罗斯油轮“Liteyny Prospect”号已停靠在河北省沧州市附近的中国黄骅港，将卸掉70万桶俄罗斯索科尔原油货物。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 08:20:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/sanctioned-tanker-liteyny-prospect-docks-china-offload-russian-oil-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>印度卢比看涨头寸达到两年多高位；路透调查：亚洲外汇空头坚守阵地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/bullish-positions-indian-rupee-over-two-year-high-asian-fx-bears-hold-ground-2024-03-07/</link><description>路透周四的一项调查显示，由于中国经济复苏的不确定性和全球货币宽松时间表拖延，印度卢比的看涨押注达到两年半以来的最高水平，而投资者对大多数亚洲货币维持看跌头寸。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:47:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/bullish-positions-indian-rupee-over-two-year-high-asian-fx-bears-hold-ground-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>马来西亚总理表示，试图遏制中国只会加剧其不满</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/trying-contain-china-will-only-fuel-its-grievances-says-malaysian-pm-2024-03-07/</link><description>马来西亚总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣周四在澳大利亚发表讲话时表示，遏制中国崛起的企图只会加剧该国的局势，并在该地区制造不和。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:38:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/trying-contain-china-will-only-fuel-its-grievances-says-malaysian-pm-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>日本表示对中俄更密切的军事关系感到严重关切</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan-says-it-is-gravely-concerned-about-closer-military-ties-between-china-2024-03-07/</link><description>日本政府最高发言人周四表示，考虑到日本和该地区的安全，东京对中俄之间更密切的军事合作表示严重关切。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 07:24:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan-says-it-is-gravely-concerned-about-closer-military-ties-between-china-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>随着大型科技公司争先恐后地遵守欧盟规则，调查可能会发生</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/big-tech-scrambles-meet-eu-rules-investigations-seen-likely-2024-03-07/</link><description>从彻底改革在线平台到幕后工程，谷歌、苹果、亚马逊、微软、Meta 和 TikTok 所有者字节跳动在过去六个月里都在努力遵守周四生效的具有里程碑意义的欧盟技术规则。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 06:03:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/big-tech-scrambles-meet-eu-rules-investigations-seen-likely-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>立陶宛称俄罗斯可以在乌克兰继续战斗至少两年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-can-fight-ukraine-least-two-years-lithuania-says-2024-03-07/</link><description>立陶宛情报机构周四在一份报告中表示，高油价、逃避制裁和国家投资正在为俄罗斯提供足够的资源，以目前的强度在乌克兰进行至少两年的战斗。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 05:34:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-can-fight-ukraine-least-two-years-lithuania-says-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>香港法官驳回亲民主电台主持人煽动叛乱案上诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-judges-dismiss-appeal-sedition-case-pro-democracy-radio-host-2024-03-07/</link><description>周四，三名香港高等法院法官驳回了民主活动人士谭德志对其定罪和 40 个月刑期的上诉，其中包括 7 项煽动罪。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:54:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/hong-kong-judges-dismiss-appeal-sedition-case-pro-democracy-radio-host-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>全球需求回升，中国出口超预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-jan-feb-trade-beats-forecasts-signals-global-trade-rebound-2024-03-07/</link><description>中国一月至二月的进出口增长超出预期，表明全球贸易正在出现拐点，这对试图支撑步履蹒跚的经济复苏的政策制定者来说是一个令人鼓舞的信号。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:34:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-jan-feb-trade-beats-forecasts-signals-global-trade-rebound-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国1-2月出口增长7.1%，进口增长3.5%，好于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-jan-feb-exports-rise-71-imports-grow-35-beating-forecasts-2024-03-07/</link><description>海关周四公布的数据显示，1-2月中国出口同比增长7.1%，进口增长3.5%，两项数据均好于预期。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:14:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-jan-feb-exports-rise-71-imports-grow-35-beating-forecasts-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国企业集团复星旗下旅游部门表示正在审查业务组合</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-conglomerate-fosuns-tourism-unit-says-reviewing-business-portfolio-2024-03-07/</link><description>复星旅文集团周四表示，正在审查其业务组合，以回应路透社有关其正在探索出售酒店度假村的报道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:09:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-conglomerate-fosuns-tourism-unit-says-reviewing-business-portfolio-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国将向六国旅客提供免签待遇</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-offer-visa-free-travel-travellers-six-countries-2024-03-07/</link><description>外交部长王毅周四表示，中国将从3月14日起向瑞士、爱尔兰、匈牙利、奥地利、比利时和卢森堡公民提供免签旅行。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 03:05:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-offer-visa-free-travel-travellers-six-countries-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市普遍走高；日本央行的讨论提振日元，打压日经指数</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-07/</link><description>周四，亚洲股市大多上涨，原因是越来越多的迹象表明美联储将很快开始降息，投资者对此感到安慰，而有关日本即将实施政策转变的传言提振了日元，并将日经指数从历史高位拉低。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 02:35:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>外长称美国对中国有错误认知</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/us-has-wrong-perception-china-says-foreign-minister-2024-03-07/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周四表示，尽管自去年 11 月拜登总统和习近平主席会晤以来取得了一些进展，但美国仍坚持对中国的错误认知，尚未兑现其“承诺”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 02:32:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/us-has-wrong-perception-china-says-foreign-minister-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>中俄加强新型合作、巩固友谊</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-foster-new-cooperation-consolidate-friendship-with-russia-2024-03-07/</link><description>外交部长王毅在北京举行的年度议会会议期间举行的新闻发布会上表示，中方愿与俄方一道，培育合作新动能，巩固友谊。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 02:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-foster-new-cooperation-consolidate-friendship-with-russia-2024-03-07/</guid></item><item><title>乐观的中国贸易数据推动油价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-edge-higher-after-us-stocks-build-less-than-expected-2024-03-07/</link><description>周四油价保持稳定，在乐观的中国贸易数据以及美国数据显示原油库存增幅小于预期以及燃料库存大幅减少后，维持隔夜涨幅。</description><pubDate>Thu, 07 Mar 2024 01:50:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-edge-higher-after-us-stocks-build-less-than-expected-2024-03-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>